ets.<\/p><p>The product has been quite stable and that was the main strength and selling point.<\/p><p><b>They wanted to achieve the following :<\/b><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5d832c4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5d832c4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent; text-align: var(--text-align);\">The leadership team wanted to enable the Sales team with a structured approach to Sales process<span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">\u00a0offerings.<\/span><\/span><\/li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: var( --e-global-color-text ); text-align: var(--text-align);\">To create a customer-focused\u00a0<\/span>and high growth mindset sales team who can have \u201cConsultative Selling\u2019 approach with the customers.<\/li><li>The team was hard working but management wanted to bring in structure \/process to the sales team\u2019s work.<\/li><li>Improve the conversion ratio\u00a0of \u201cOpportunity to Order\u201d.<\/li><li>\u00a0Improve credibility with Mid-Senior customer touchpoints by enabling the sales team with skills to have insightful conversations with customers<\/li><li>They also wanted to create a &#8220;Common Language&#8221; across the sales team from Prospect &#8211; Order process.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-88bc9c8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"88bc9c8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Service We Provided<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2fcc0bf elementor-widge